#○	Take input from the user in two variables. Perform below operations
#■	Find remainder
#■	Perform floor division
#■	Calculate a raise to b
num1 = int(input("Enter the 1st number: "))
num2 = int(input("Enter the 2nd number: "))
print("The remainder is ", num1 % num2)
print("The floor division is ", num1 // num2)
print("The answer for the 1st number raised to 2nd number is ", num1 ** num2)
